      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS actuation. This unit has undergone extensive preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh, ensuring the 3.2L inline-six pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Performance is further refined via Bilstein adjustable coilovers, providing superior lateral stability and transient response. While the finish shows light patina commensurate with enthusiast use, the mechanical synchronization and chassis rigidity remain top-tier for the purist driver.",
